00:16:27.779 --> 00:16:28.988 position:50% align:center
[GROUP gasps]

00:16:53.096 --> 00:16:55.890 position:50% align:center
[KANATA] These five festival
days have been monumental.

00:16:55.974 --> 00:16:57.976 position:50% align:center
