wrote this number for us.

00:17:25.253 --> 00:17:27.630 position:50% align:center
We wanna dedicate
this song to you.

00:17:27.714 --> 00:17:29.132 position:50% align:center
The fans watching us.

00:17:29.215 --> 00:17:30.842 position:50% align:center
If it wasn't for your support,

00:17:30.925 --> 00:17:33.428 position:50% align:center
we wouldn't be on
this stage tonight.

00:17:33.511 --> 00:17:35.305 position:50% align:center
You're the ones
who give us strength.

00:17:35.388 --> 00:17:37.891 position:50% align:center
The whole reason we
threw this festival.

00:17:37.974 --> 00:17:41.102 position:50% align:center
We're idols because
of our audience.

00:17:41.186 --> 00:17:43.897 position:50% align:center
And everyone who helped
this song come to life.

00:17:43.980 --> 00:17:46.775 position:50% align:center
This festival only
started as an idea.

00:17:46.858 --> 00:17:50.320 position:50% align:center
And was successful because
of immense dedication.

00:17:50.403 --> 00:17:52.822 position:50% align:center
[EMMA] Getting to see so
many amazing performances

00:17:52.906 --> 00:17:54.366 position:50% align:center
