00:18:13.051 --> 00:18:17.514 position:50% align:center
It may be ending, but our
next dream is just beginning.

00:18:17.597 --> 00:18:22.769 position:50% align:center
We hope you'll be a part of it.
Join us on our journey.

00:18:22.852 --> 00:18:25.105 position:50% align:center
Starting with this new song.

00:18:46.960 --> 00:18:50.922 position:50% align:center
[inhales, exhales]

00:20:49.249 --> 00:20:55.422 position:50% align:center
[STUDENTS cheering]

00:20:55.505 --> 00:20:57.674 position:50% align:center
[YU laughing]

00:21:25.577 --> 00:21:27.328 position:50% align:center
[laughs]

00:23:05.218 --> 00:23:07.137 position:50% align:center
[GROUP]
Cheers!

00:23:07.220 --> 00:23:09.848 position:50% align:center
[VICE PRESIDENT A]
You were truly awe-inspiring!

00:23:09.931 --> 00:23:11.224 position:50% align:center
Aw, gee, thanks!

00:23:11.307 --> 00:23:12.225 position:50% align:center
[LANZHU speaking in Chinese]

00:23:12.308 --> 00:23:13.560 position:50% align:center
[GROUP gasps]

00:23:13.643 --> 00:23:14.686 position:50% align:center
[AYUMU]
Lanzhu!

